snippet.title: Saqib Hussain
snippet.description:
Hi there and Welcome to my channel ,
           
My name is Saqib Hussain and i am an artist . I have been doing art since i was a child and now it has been 12 years  that i have been working for cg industry.

And now i think its the best time to  share my knowledge with you. 

This is the channel where i will be making tutorials where you will learn about 3D or 2D art whether it is for Games or for Film purpose.

Tutorials will include 3D Modelling , Texturing , Rendering , Animation ,Rigging , UV mapping , Baking . 

So Subscribe and Share if you want to get more from me .
